<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WeighGuard - Notifications</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin/adminUsers.css">
</head>
<body class="flex h-screen overflow-hidden bg-slate-950 font-sans text-slate-300">

    <%- include('../partials/adminHeaderSidebar', { currentPage: currentPage }) %>

    <main class="flex-1 flex flex-col overflow-hidden relative bg-slate-950">
        
        <header class="h-20 bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-800 flex items-center justify-between px-8 shrink-0 z-10 sticky top-0">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">Notification Management</h1>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-medium mt-0.5">Receive system messages in real time and manage announcements.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <button onclick="markAllAsRead()" class="bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-white px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-slate-700 transition shadow-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    Mark all as read
                </button>
                <button onclick="openModal('createAnnouncementModal')" class="bg-emerald-500 text-slate-900 px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs font-extrabold flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-emerald-400 transition shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(52,211,153,0.4)] uppercase tracking-wide">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11 5.882V19.24a1.76 1.76 0 01-3.417.592l-2.147-6.15M18 13a3 3 0 100-6M5.436 13.683A4.001 4.001 0 017 6h1.832c4.1 0 7.625-1.234 9.168-3v14c-1.543-1.766-5.067-3-9.168-3H7a3.988 3.988 0 01-1.564-.317z"></path></svg>
                    Create Announcement
                </button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="flex-1 overflow-hidden p-8 flex flex-col space-y-6">
            
            <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 shadow-lg flex flex-col shrink-0 overflow-hidden">
                
                <div class="flex border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50">
                    <button id="tabInbox" onclick="switchTab('inbox')" class="flex-1 py-4 text-sm font-bold border-b-2 border-emerald-400 text-emerald-400 transition bg-emerald-500/5">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 13V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v7m16 0v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5m16 0h-2.586a1 1 0 00-.707.293l-2.414 2.414a1 1 0 01-.707.293h-3.172a1 1 0 01-.707-.293l-2.414-2.414A1 1 0 006.586 13H4"></path></svg>
                            Inbox
                            <span class="bg-rose-500 text-white text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full leading-none ml-1 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(244,63,94,0.6)]">3</span>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                    <button id="tabSent" onclick="switchTab('sent')" class="flex-1 py-4 text-sm font-bold border-b-2 border-transparent text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-300 transition hover:bg-slate-800/30">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 19l9 2-9-18-9 18 9-2zm0 0v-8"></path></svg>
                            Sent History
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="p-5 px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-between items-center">
                    <div class="relative w-full md:w-96 group">
                        <span class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 flex items-center pl-3.5 pointer-events-none">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-500 group-focus-within:text-emerald-400 transition-colors" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path></svg>
                        </span>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Search notifications..." class="w-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-700 text-sm rounded-xl pl-10 pr-4 py-2.5 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500/20 focus:border-emerald-500 text-slate-200 transition-all placeholder-slate-500 shadow-inner">
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-3 w-full md:w-auto">
                        <select class="bg-slate-950 border border-slate-700 text-xs font-bold text-slate-300 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 focus:outline-none focus:border-emerald-500 appearance-none shadow-inner cursor-pointer flex-1">
                            <option>All Categories</option>
                            <option>System Alerts</option>
                            <option>Incident Updates</option>
                            <option>Announcements</option>
                        </select>
                        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute right-10 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 flex items-center text-slate-500 hidden md:block"><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 shadow-lg flex flex-col overflow-hidden flex-1">
                <div class="overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar h-full">
                    
                    <table id="inboxTable" class="w-full text-left border-collapse whitespace-nowrap">
                        <thead class="sticky top-0 bg-slate-900/90 backdrop-blur border-b border-slate-800 z-10">
                            <tr class="text-slate-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
                                <th class="px-6 py-4 w-8"></th>
                                <th class="px-6 py-4">Notification Details</th>
                                <th class="px-6 py-4">Category</th>
                                <th class="px-6 py-4">Received</th>
                                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-right">Action</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-800/50">
                            
                            <tr class="bg-blue-500/5 hover:bg-blue-500/10 transition-colors group cursor-pointer" onclick="openModal('viewNotificationModal')">
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(59,130,246,0.8)] animate-pulse"></div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <div class="text-sm font-extrabold text-white">System Maintenance Scheduled</div>
                                    <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-0.5 truncate max-w-md">Servers will undergo routine maintenance at 02:00 AM PHT. Expect 15 mins of downtime.</div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 text-slate-300 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">System</span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase">
                                    10 mins ago
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right">
                                    <button class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-800" title="View"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path></svg></button>
                                </td>
                            </tr>

                            <tr class="bg-rose-500/5 hover:bg-rose-500/10 transition-colors group cursor-pointer" onclick="openModal('viewNotificationModal')">
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-rose-500 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(244,63,94,0.8)] animate-pulse"></div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <div class="text-sm font-extrabold text-rose-400">Cargo Loss Detected: RC-0034</div>
                                    <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-0.5 truncate max-w-md">Vehicle RC-0034 has reported a sudden weight drop of 15kg. Action required.</div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-rose-500/10 border border-rose-500/20 text-rose-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Alert</span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase">
                                    1 hour ago
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right">
                                    <button class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-800" title="View"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path></svg></button>
                                </td>
                            </tr>

                            <tr class="hover:bg-slate-800/40 transition-colors group cursor-pointer" onclick="openModal('viewNotificationModal')">
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <div class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-300">New Driver Account Created</div>
                                    <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5 truncate max-w-md">Account for "Sarah Connor" has been successfully provisioned.</div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Admin</span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500 uppercase">
                                    Yesterday
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right">
                                    <button class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-800" title="View"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path></svg></button>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>

                    <table id="sentTable" class="w-full text-left border-collapse whitespace-nowrap hidden">
                        <thead class="sticky top-0 bg-slate-900/90 backdrop-blur border-b border-slate-800 z-10">
                            <tr class="text-slate-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
                                <th class="px-6 py-4">Announcement Details</th>
                                <th class="px-6 py-4">Target Audience</th>
                                <th class="px-6 py-4">Sent Date</th>
                                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-right">Action</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-800/50">
                            <tr class="hover:bg-slate-800/40 transition-colors group cursor-pointer" onclick="openModal('viewNotificationModal')">
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <div class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Weather Advisory: Heavy Rain</div>
                                    <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5 truncate max-w-md">Please reduce speeds by 20% in Zone B due to severe weather conditions.</div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">All Drivers</span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500 uppercase">
                                    Oct 12, 2025
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-right">
                                    <button class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-800" title="View"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path></svg></button>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div id="modalOverlay" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-sm z-40 hidden opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300" onclick="closeAllModals()"></div>

    <div id="createAnnouncementModal" class="fixed top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-50 w-full max-w-2xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl hidden opacity-0 scale-95 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-8 py-6 border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 flex items-center justify-center border border-emerald-500/20 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(52,211,153,0.2)]">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11 5.882V19.24a1.76 1.76 0 01-3.417.592l-2.147-6.15M18 13a3 3 0 100-6M5.436 13.683A4.001 4.001 0 017 6h1.832c4.1 0 7.625-1.234 9.168-3v14c-1.543-1.766-5.067-3-9.168-3H7a3.988 3.988 0 01-1.564-.317z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">Create Announcement</h2>
            </div>
            <button onclick="closeModal('createAnnouncementModal')" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 p-2 rounded-xl transition"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path></svg></button>
        </div>
        
        <form class="p-8 space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Target Audience</label>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <select class="w-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-700 text-white text-sm rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 focus:outline-none focus:border-emerald-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-500 transition shadow-inner appearance-none cursor-pointer">
                            <option>All Users</option>
                            <option>Active Drivers Only</option>
                            <option>System Admins</option>
                        </select>
                        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 right-4 flex items-center text-slate-500"><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Priority Level</label>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <select class="w-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-700 text-white text-sm rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 focus:outline-none focus:border-emerald-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-500 transition shadow-inner appearance-none cursor-pointer">
                            <option>Normal (Info)</option>
                            <option class="text-amber-400">High (Warning)</option>
                            <option class="text-rose-400">Critical (Alert)</option>
                        </select>
                        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 right-4 flex items-center text-slate-500"><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-span-2">
                    <label class="block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Subject Line</label>
                    <input type="text" class="w-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-700 text-white text-sm rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 focus:outline-none focus:border-emerald-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-500 transition shadow-inner" placeholder="E.g., System Update, Weather Warning...">
                </div>
                <div class="col-span-2">
                    <label class="block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Message Body</label>
                    <textarea class="w-full bg-slate-950 border border-slate-700 text-white text-sm rounded-xl px-4 py-3.5 focus:outline-none focus:border-emerald-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-500 transition shadow-inner custom-scrollbar" rows="5" placeholder="Type your announcement here..."></textarea>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-800 flex gap-4 mt-2">
                <button type="button" onclick="closeModal('createAnnouncementModal')" class="w-1/3 py-3.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 text-slate-300 font-bold hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-white transition">Cancel</button>
                <button type="button" onclick="closeModal('createAnnouncementModal')" class="w-2/3 py-3.5 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-400 text-slate-900 font-extrabold transition shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(52,211,153,0.4)] tracking-wide uppercase text-xs flex justify-center items-center gap-2">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 19l9 2-9-18-9 18 9-2zm0 0v-8"></path></svg>
                    Send Announcement
                </button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div id="viewNotificationModal" class="fixed top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-50 w-full max-w-lg bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl hidden opacity-0 scale-95 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-8 py-6 border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 flex justify-between items-start">
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                    <span class="px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">System</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500 uppercase">Oct 12, 10:30 AM</span>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">System Maintenance Scheduled</h2>
            </div>
            <button onclick="closeModal('viewNotificationModal')" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 p-2 rounded-xl transition"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path></svg></button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-8">
            <div class="bg-slate-950 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 shadow-inner">
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                    Hello Team,<br><br>
                    Please be advised that the WeighGuard central servers will undergo routine maintenance at 02:00 AM PHT tonight. <br><br>
                    During this time, the Live Map and Incident Logging features will experience intermittent connectivity for approximately 15 minutes. Data collection on the edge devices will continue normally and sync once the servers are back online.<br><br>
                    Thank you,<br>System Administrator
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-6 mt-6 flex justify-end">
                <button type="button" onclick="closeModal('viewNotificationModal')" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 text-slate-300 font-bold hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-white transition">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/admin/adminNotification.js"></script>
</body>
</html>